 illuminate the world's path to a brighter and more harmonious future.\", \"from\": 854, \"to\": 1017, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 867, \"end\": 871, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saarland\", \"score\": 0.7322296036658433, \"rank\": 0.3591540544174223, \"text\": \"Saar\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saarland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saarland\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The piece\", \"from\": 854, \"to\": 863}, {\"ngram\": \"a female figure\", \"from\": 887, \"to\": 902}, {\"ngram\": \"a flame\", \"from\": 913, \"to\": 920}, {\"ngram\": \"a beacon\", \"from\": 936, \"to\": 944}, {\"ngram\": \"the world's path\", \"from\": 959, \"to\": 975}, {\"ngram\": \"a brighter and more harmonious future\", \"from\": 979, \"to\": 1016}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Sport, much like art, is about capturing the hearts and minds of people with inspirational accomplishments,\\\" Bach said.\", \"from\": 1019, \"to\": 1139, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1129, \"end\": 1133, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\", \"score\": 0.9999999998624389, \"rank\": 1.3745241514479534e-10, \"text\": \"Bach\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Sport\", \"from\": 1020, \"to\": 1025}, {\"ngram\": \"art\", \"from\": 1037, \"to\": 1040}, {\"ngram\": \"the hearts\", \"from\": 1061, \"to\": 1071}, {\"ngram\": \"minds\", \"from\": 1076, \"to\": 1081}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1085, \"to\": 1091}, {\"ngram\": \"inspirational accomplishments\", \"from\": 1097, \"to\": 1126}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Thank you, dear Alison (Saar), for your contribution to blend sport and culture in such a magnificent way.\", \"from\": 1140, \"to\": 1247, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1165, \"end\": 1169, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saarland\", \"score\": 0.7322296036658433, \"rank\": 0.3591540544174223, \"text\": \"Saar\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saarland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saarland\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your contribution\", \"from\": 1176, \"to\": 1193}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 1203, \"to\": 1208}, {\"ngram\": \"culture\", \"from\": 1213, \"to\": 1220}, {\"ngram\": \"such a magnificent way\", \"from\": 1224, \"to\": 1246}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is also what the Olympic Games are about \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093 to bring all the different cultures of the world together in a peaceful competition \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093 and for dialogue.\\\"\", \"from\": 1248, \"to\": 1404, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 1266, \"to\": 1283}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093\", \"from\": 1294, \"to\": 1297}, {\"ngram\": \"all the different cultures\", \"from\": 1307, \"to\": 1333}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 1337, \"to\": 1346}, {\"ngram\": \"a peaceful competition\", \"from\": 1359, \"to\": 1381}, {\"ngram\": \"dialogue\", \"from\": 1394, \"to\": 1402}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Salon rises from our past histories, representing our present and the urgent need for peace and dignity for all,\\\" Saar said.\", \"from\": 1406, \"to\": 1531, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1521, \"end\": 1525, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saarland\", \"score\": 0.7322296036658433, \"rank\": 0.3591540544174223, \"text\": \"Saar\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saarland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saarland\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Salon\", \"from\": 1407, \"to\": 1412}, {\"ngram\": \"our past histories\", \"from\": 1424, \"to\": 1442}, {\"ngram\": \"our present\", \"from\": 1457, \"to\": 1468}, {\"ngram\": \"the urgent need\", \"from\": 1473, \"to\": 1488}, {\"ngram\": \"peace\", \"from\": 1493, \"to\": 1498}, {\"ngram\": \"dignity\", \"from\": 1503, \"to\": 1510}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"A female figure sits in the center of the work, and in the palm of her hand, she conjures a flame, a beacon that illuminates our path towards a brighter and more harmonious future.\", \"from\": 1532, \"to\": 1713, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A female figure\", \"from\": 1533, \"to\": 1548}, {\"ngram\": \"the center\", \"from\": 1557, \"to\": 1567}, {\"ngram\": \"the work\", \"from\": 1571, \"to\": 1579}, {\"ngram\": \"the palm\", \"from\": 1588, \"to\": 1596}, {\"ngram\": \"her hand\", \"from\": 1600, \"to\": 1608}, {\"ngram\": \"a flame\", \"from\": 1623, \"to\": 1630}, {\"ngram\": \"a beacon\", \"from\": 1632, \"to\": 1640}, {\"ngram\": \"our path\", \"from\": 1658, \"to\": 1666}, {\"ngram\": \"a brighter and more harmonious future\", \"from\": 1675, \"to\": 1712}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In her other hand, she holds olive branches, a metaphor for peace and reconciliation.\", \"from\": 1714, \"to\": 1799, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her other hand\", \"from\": 1717, \"to\": 1731}, {\"ngram\": \"olive branches\", \"from\": 1743, \"to\": 1757}, {\"ngram\": \"a metaphor\", \"from\": 1759, \"to\": 1769}, {\"ngram\": \"peace\", \"from\": 1774, \"to\": 1779}, {\"ngram\": \"reconciliation\", \"from\": 1784, \"to\": 1798}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Encircled by six chairs, she invites us to sit together to represent the diversity of cultures, to share our common experiences and humanity.\\\"\", \"from\": 1800, \"to\": 1942, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"six chairs\", \"from\": 1813, \"to\": 1823}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1837, \"to\": 1839}, {\"ngram\": \"the diversity\", \"from\": 1869, \"to\": 1882}, {\"ngram\": \"cultures\", \"from\": 1886, \"to\": 1894}, {\"ngram\": \"our common experiences\", \"from\": 1905, \"to\": 1927}, {\"ngram\": \"humanity\", \"from\": 1932, \"to\": 1940}]}, {\"sentence\": \"SITEMAP EXPLORE MORE DOWNLOAD